Berlusconi Says ‘For Sure’ His Government Will Last to 2013

-- B y   C h i a r a   V a s a r r i
-- 
2011-10-22T17:53:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/berlusconi-says-for-sure-his-government-will-last-to-2013.html
Italian Prime Minister  Silvio Berlusconi  said “that’s for sure,” when asked if his embattled
government will last until the end of its term in 2013. He spoke
to reporters in Brussels today on the eve of a European Union
summit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chiara Vasarri in Milan at 
 cvasarri@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
